These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, asparagus, blueberry, garlic
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, lizard, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, golf, baseball, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the owner of the cat##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the far left##1
4. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the ferret is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person eating asparagus##2
6. the person who's sport is golf is the owner of the lizard##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | blueberry | garlic  | asparagus | artichoke  |
| Pet         | turtle    | ferret  | cat       | lizard     |
| Sport   | baseball     | volleyball | snowboarding       | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, drawing, magic-tricks, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, sports, superhero, zombie
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, dannemann, vegafina, blend
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the blend-smoker is between the person watching zombie movies and the person who's hobby is reading##2
5. the person watching zombie movies is the dannemann-smoker##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | drawing | chess    | reading  | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | fantasy  | sports   | superhero    |
| Cigar         | dannemann | blend | tiparillo | vegafina      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, sprite, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, gardening, photography
4 different pets are kept: rat, fish, pony, lizard
1. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the lizard and the person drinking mirinda##2
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | tea         | lemonade   | sprite    |
| Hobby         | cooking | photography | collecting | gardening |
| Pet   | pony   | fish        | lizard      | rat   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, dutch, german, polish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, skateboarding, tennis
City: colone, hamburg, london, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to colone is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the polish##2
3. the german is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the german is on the right of the australian##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person traveling to hamburg##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | polish        | dutch   | australian | german |
| Sport         | skateboarding | cricket | cycling    | tennis |
| City     | london       | colone     | edinburgh       | hamburg    |

