.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, cooking, sudoku
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, spy, western
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, tiparillo, davidoff, swisher
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the person watching crime movies is between the swisher-smoker and the person who's hobby is camping##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku  | camping | cooking | board-games |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | western | crime   | spy         |
| Cigar           | fonseca | davidoff  | tiparillo   | swisher      |

