.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, aristoff, game, vegafina
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, puzzles, reading
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, guinea-pig, rat
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the owner of the dog is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the owner of the dog and the vegafina-smoker##2
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the owner of the rat##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the owner of the goat##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar    | vegafina  | game | bolivar | aristoff     |
| Hobby   | board-games | puzzles   | reading  | camping    |
| Pet     | goat        | rat       | dog      | guinea-pig |

