.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, milk, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, filmmaking, hiking, reading
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, hip-hop, funk, rock
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of rock is between the person drinking milk and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is the fan of funk##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
6. the person drinking water is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | water  | milk       | fanta   |
| Hobby      | drawing     | hiking | filmmaking | reading |
| Music-Genre        | funk        | rock | salsa     | hip-hop |

