4 different pets are kept: rat, bird, dog, mouse
There are 4 different nationalities: german, indian, italian, mexican
1. the owner of the rat is the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking mirinda and the indian##2
3. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the bird##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is between the owner of the dog and the mexican##2
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the german is between the italian and the owner of the mouse##2
7. the owner of the rat is the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | mirinda | cola   | soy-milk |
| Pet   | rat  | bird    | dog   | mouse     |
| Nationality   | mexican  | italian | german | indian   |

